text: ( Source : Government of Nova Scotia ) Premier Stephen McNeil welcomed the arrival of Shell Canada 's offshore drilling vessel Stena IceMAX to Nova Scotia 's waters today, Oct. 20. The vessel, owned by Stena Drilling of Aberdeen, Scotland ,
